⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Sam Cortland
node M1 · M1 · ⟦Sam Cortland:M1:fcaca2⟧

WHO   — Sam Cortland — Assassin of the Guild · Celaena's partner
WHAT  — The deuteragonist of The Assassin's Blade — a gifted, principled killer who chooses tenderness over the cruelty he was trained into, and whose murder is the loss that breaks Celaena and delivers her to Endovier.
WHERE — M1 · Maas  Framework inputs: Throne of Glass — The Assassin's Blade  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because the Guild owns its people but not their hearts; because a price can be saved coin by coin until two killers walk free; because some things — and someone — are worth defying the King of the Assassins for.
HOW   — By blade and stealth equal to Celaena's own, learned under the same brutal master; by a steadiness and decency that the Guild never beat out of him; by the courage to stand against Arobynn when standing meant death.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  I can't remember a time when I didn't know you.

